{"tid":286784,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（回憶postcard行動）紅色的郵筒就像是帶着神秘","createTime":"2017-06-17T00:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T15:13:55.000Z","uid":72153,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"996d6ff54bb89e43fef19a8a18caf10c597bbfc0","tid":286784,"uid":72153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"有幸在另一面旗幟下生活了10多年。20年了，那些記憶雖然褪色，但那鮮明的顔色還在腦海裏。曾經，曾經郵政服務和消防救護都是同一顏色，20年前，卻換上男人最討厭的顏色。<br />\n<br />\n今天郵局可以因為收入不好關閉，老人因為賣紙皮被罰款。換走一面旗幟，連靈魂都換走了。<br />\n<br />\n我不能幫郵筒換回本來的衣服，我只能透過科技把以前的樣子略為還原。<br />\n<br />\n我要把這59個政府想除之而後快的郵筒記錄下來，不知道下個20年還留下多少？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMD8A5B4rGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMD8A5B4rGE&d=HM8LQO%2Fvgatu%2FKS7ZQBz8QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=495c9d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMD8A5B4rGE</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rFbbA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rFbbA8&d=HM8LQO%2Fvgatu%2FKS7ZQBz8QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=afa7f4c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rFbbA8</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram: HappymomentHK <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/084212_17ac2704af0287c0fdbe60d741251cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F084212_17ac2704af0287c0fdbe60d741251cca.jpg&h=4aa841c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71f15ae9d67864f4a9ecf9fedcde7e6167a2c672","tid":286784,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f22777a46146505e454c8995622b32b561f045d","tid":286784,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40d70c3f402714825627670977ffcded48368bb0","tid":286784,"uid":33952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:14:53.000Z","msg":"邱通"},{"pid":"5ebd4de442a5d2b074f3b0a8