rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36e22c7725f262507baf613883c5b9909b8cf71","tid":286784,"uid":72153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然得7views?係咪直接係到睇唔計views<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想要啊 巴打會唔會考慮下降低少少views數 好可惜啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw 可以話我知呢d郵筒係邊嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你。這個在油塘，其實影片已經有提示。巴打可以分享俾朋友。postcard 已印好，view數只是一個動力，畢竟拍哂59個郵筒要大家集氣。就算不夠10,000 view 也會送出postcard 。"},{"pid":"1437b1182695ceb9a5003c347a0c3a5668d56914","tid":286784,"uid":72153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/185216_a7a3651ad94865d153be578317fcd03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F185216_a7a3651ad94865d153be578317fcd03a.jpg&h=51a31311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a888cfd6261eed2a95dbaac69fdeef618165a2b","tid":286784,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"86a51834a788d4cc5e44eafc58fb5e83ec4cebbc","tid":286784,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時起我都好鍾意郵筒<br />\n<br />\n寄信俾人同期待回信呢啲嘢真係俱往矣<br />\n<br />\n巴打繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eecfe7a023b137dd8c72c7ebe29dda686b6c09e","tid":286784,"uid":8559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"得閒去油塘睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f459e797630cf87e0d0bcfa5e8d58fd8ebf02e","tid":286784,"uid":72153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT